{
  "texts": [
    "Nevertheless the classifier results can be interpreted as the best-guess inferences that a human would make: the guesses from the LLM correlate highly with human guesses from the same prompt, and we get similar qualitative results when the prompt includes a third category for \"uncertain.\"",
    "5.1 What share of ChatGPT queries are related to paid work?",
    "We label each user message in our dataset based on whether it appears to be related to work, using an LLM classifier.",
    "The critical part of the prompt is as follows: 21 Does the last user message of this conversation transcript seem likely to be related to doing some work/employment?",
    "Answer with one of the following:"
  ]
}